Class ChunkSamplerImpl

java.lang.Object
  EObjectImpl

All Implemented Interfaces:
Chunk, ChunkSampler
public class ChunkSamplerImpl
extends ChunkImpl
implements ChunkSampler

An implementation of the model object 'Chunk Sampler'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Manufacturer
  • Product
  • Sample Period
  • Midi Unity Note
  • Midi Pitch Fraction
  • Smpte Format
  • Smpte Offset
  • Number Of Sample Loops
  • Sampler Data Size
  • Sample Loops
  • Sampler Data
